  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d0a663575cba5a64886a6bdb08734bb7, type: 3}
  m_Name: WinDialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  speakerName: Whim
  lines:
  - The ache in your head goes away. Every limb that felt as though it were growing
    distant returns to you. The parasite fungus, its network structure vaguely in
    the shape of you, hits the ground before you ineffectually.
  - "\u201COh, wonderful~! You do have potential after all! Now that we have the
    time for introductions, my name is Whim. I\u2019m aware you don\u2019t have a
    name. We\u2019ll find you one later.\u201D"
  - "\u201CNow, don\u2019t bask in your freedom too long. You owe me, remember?\u201D"
  - "\u201CHow would you like to purify the entire forest for me?\u201D"
  - You Win!
  triggerKey: Finish
  nextNode: {fileID: 0}
  onComplete:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  typingSpeed: 0.05
  autoProgressDelay: 1.5
